race.description: Parkes Courier Service / Mca Engineering Handicap
race.comment: IN THE NIC OF TIME (3) was an effortless winner last time over this track and trip when leading all the way. This is obviously tougher but he should be able to offset the wide draw quickly and give another great sight. FEIMAZUO (2) has been thereabouts in her two runs back and have finished full of running. Nearing peak now and will appreciate the added trip. Gallagher reuniting is another positive. Big threat. ALPINE ROSE (9) raced on the speed from the outset last start and finished second over 1800m at Gilgandra. Has found form and is sure to give another strong account. Have to include. YIASOU (5) has plenty of early dash and is sure to take another strong account.
